text: Klaus-Dieter Bähr (born 9 September 1941) is a German rower who represented East Germany. He competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics in Mexico City with the men's eight where they came seventh. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Rowers from Berlin Category:German male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of East Germany Category:Rowers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:World Rowing Championships medalists for East Germany Category:European Rowing Championships medalists
